SUMMARY:Easy Run — 3 miles
DESCRIPTION:Run type: Easy\nDistance: 3 miles\nEffort: RPE 3–4/10\n\nInst
 ructions\nKeep this conversational. In Maryland heat\, slow down as much
  as needed.\n\nOptional\nAdd 4 x 20 sec relaxed strides only if you feel
  good.\n\nDo not\nTurn this into a tempo run.
LOCATION:
CATEGORIES:RUN
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
