 ill\n4 x 50 smooth\n100–200 continuous very easy\n50 cooldown\n\nGoal\nL
 eave the pool fresh and confident.
LOCATION:Indoor pool
CATEGORIES:SWIM
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
